name: djvulibre
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "djvulibre" %}
{% set version = "3.5.28" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://downloads.sourceforge.net/project/djvu/DjVuLibre/{{ version }}/djvulibre-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: fcd009ea7654fde5a83600eb80757bd3a76998e47d13c66b54c8db849f8f2edc

build:
  skip: true  # [win]
  number: 0

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ compiler('c') }}
    - {{ compiler('cxx') }}
    - autoconf
    - automake
    - libtool
    - pkg-config
    - make
  host:
    - librsvg
    - libtiff
    - libjpeg-turbo
    - jpeg
  run:
    - libjpeg-turbo
    - libtiff
    - jpeg

test:
  commands:
    - ddjvu --help 2>&1 >/dev/null | grep Usage

about:
  home: http://djvu.sourceforge.net/
  license:  GPL-2.0-only
  license_file: COPYING
  summary: Suite to create, manipulate and view DjVu ('déjà vu') documents

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - izahn
